    {"book":"1 Kings","chapter":22,"verses":[{"verse":14,"reason":"Micaiah's declaration: 'What the LORD saith unto me, that will I speak'—unwavering prophetic integrity."},{"verse":17,"reason":"Micaiah's vision of Israel scattered as sheep without a shepherd—prophetic imagery echoed by Jesus."}]}
